# Minimal sbagenxlib keyframed sequence format (Phase 3.3)
# <time><optional-unit> <tone-spec>
#
# Units:
#   (none) or s = seconds
#   m = minutes
#   h = hours
#
# Tone-specs:
#   binaural   carrier+beat/amp
#   monaural   carrierMbeat/amp
#   isochronic carrier@pulse/amp

0s     200+10/20 ramp
30s    190+8/20
60s    180+6/20
